1️⃣Hardware Requirements

Computer/Laptop (Minimum 4 GB RAM recommended)

10 GB free disk space

Internet connection (for dataset download & libraries)

2️⃣ Software Requirements
Operating System

Windows 10 / 11

Linux

macOS

(Works on any OS because Python is cross-platform)

Programming Language

Python 3.8 or above

Python Libraries

Add these inside requirements.txt

pandas
numpy
matplotlib
jupyter
seaborn

3️⃣ Dataset Requirements

The dataset must contain:

Column	Description
Date	Transaction date
Customer ID	Unique customer
Gender	Male/Female
Age	Customer age
Product Category	Product type
Quantity	Units purchased
Price per Unit	Item cost
Total Amount	Final bill
4️⃣ Functional Requirements

The system should:

Load dataset

Clean missing values

Convert datatypes

Calculate total sales

Analyze sales by category

Analyze customer behavior

Identify top customers

Generate monthly trends

Display graphs

5️⃣ Non-Functional Requirements

Fast execution (<5 seconds for small dataset)

Accurate calculations

Easy to understand visualizations

Reusable code structure
